name: Maison Balzac La Rose Glass Candle
description:
Handmade 'La Rose' perfumed soy candle from Maison Balzac. 

Size: 9cm (high) 7cm (diameter) 175g 
Burning time: Approx. 40 hours, pure cotton wick

This beautiful candle captures the essence of a French garden filled with roses and delicate violets. With essential oils like Tea Rose, Violet Leaf, Rose Geranium and Rosewood you'll be whisked away to a sun-drenched garden in a moment. 

Glass can be re-used; makes an ideal vase or even pencil holder. Handmade in Australia.

Add Maison Balzac's glass dome to complete the look and keep your candle dust-free. 

Four perfumed scents available - Le Soleil, Le Bois, LEglise, La Rose
